{"tid":998760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩綠van線引入支那寶　料半年內擴至逾70條線　長者2元乘車優惠不適用","createTime":"2019-01-28T08:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T02:54:28.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2c2b49e3f5b2241350cf3ace4e7242b3516250","tid":998760,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190128/s00001/c1aa50c79bc47314b7f38d5f23e30f41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2Fc1aa50c79bc47314b7f38d5f23e30f41.jpg&h=1fcf8501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有專線小巴營辦商引入電子錢包支付車資，乘客可透過智能電話使用AlipayHK，讓小巴上的裝置掃描手機上的二維碼，就完成支付，惟支付寶付款不適用於長者2元乘車優惠。<br />\n<br />\n最先推出電子錢包支付的是來往碧瑤灣及中環交易廣場的專線小巴8和8X，營辦商進智公交行政總裁陳文俊表示，在3至6個月內會將電子錢包支付引入全線70多條路線，但現階段未能估計使用電子支付的乘客數目。<br />\n<br />\nAlipay Payment Services行政總裁陳婉真表示，預計今年內在九龍、新界亦會有專線小巴使用支付寶支付車資，正與巴士、渡輪等不同公共交通工具營辦商討論合作，希望年內可落實在巴士上接受支付寶付車資，但未有透露手續費、租機費等細節。她又說，現時小巴支付暫時只接受香港版支付寶，未來會開放內地版支付寶使用。<br />\n<br />\n不過，現時使用支付寶在小巴支付車資，並不能使用長者2元乘車優惠，立法會議員易志明表示，會要求政府將優惠擴至電子支付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190128/s00001/1548660815642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2F1548660815642&d=wuRAGhAhlQknfzdK5YHn87%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=62d56c10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2F1548660815642&h=ecae1f56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190128/s00001/1548660815642</a>"},{"pid":"03963363c7d9398c056cebe657c2a418f3c50b5b","tid":998760,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔拎走部八達通機或者長期半價去補貼用戶, 以半迫半推既模式去推行既話我諗有排都唔會流行. 即使唔抗拒既中年人好多都唔識用"},{"pid":"6884ba071183c8f3eb7147a53a0d13834534e268","tid":998760,"uid":96231,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"做咩要阻住小巴佬開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前嘟八達通都有個譜，起碼磨手袋點都磨到出黎<br />\n依家支那寶 一部iphone 5 同埋一位手腳慢嘅就仆街㗎啦"},{"pid":"f17b7933646341708f002f71e2fd1867c508b005","tid":998760,"uid":147367,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"小巴佬怒氣值將會急速上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6394bd57fcc12fe1875cd5f58d5cbfe542a544c","tid":998760,"uid":29625,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f17b7933646341708f002f71e2fd1867c508b005","tid":998760,"uid":147367,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"小巴佬怒氣值將會急速上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"過一排就會貼張紙寫壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b40b4517980060230412221b8bbccdff6a734d","tid":998760,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6394bd57fcc12fe1875cd5f58d5cbfe542a544c","tid":998760,"uid":29625,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f17b7933646341708f002f71e2fd1867c508b005","tid":998760,"uid":147367,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"小巴佬怒氣值將會急速上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"過一排就會貼張紙寫壞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"希望係咁 咁就係支那宝敗退之時"},{"pid":"2c62b2105402f5a143e76deaf7635ff59a86cf7e","tid":998760,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6394bd57fcc12fe1875cd5f58d5cbfe542a544c","tid":998760,"uid":29625,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f17b7933646341708f002f71e2fd1867c508b005","tid":998760,"u